long_description: Clocks play a very important role in everyone's home and their daily lives. Our Blue, red, Green & brown Royal, and Elegant Flower design Decorative Papier-Mache Wooden Handcrafted Wall Clock is the best papier mache wall clock that you can have a hold of, which comes in Blue, red, green, and brown colors. This also stands as a great gift option for your friends and family at several events.
